# EduLens – AI Student Analytics Platform

EduLens is a full-stack AI-powered dashboard that helps educators identify at-risk students using machine learning and AI explanations.

## Features
- Student data management API
- ML-based risk prediction
- AI assistant for insights (LLM)
- Interactive dashboard (React)

## Tech Stack
- FastAPI, MongoDB, Scikit-learn
- React (Vite)
- Groq LLM

